cdata.name: Divi Project
cdata.desc:
Divi Project is a cryptocurrency financial platform. It enables users to accessa set of financial tools where it is possible to perform cryptocurrency transactions or store, monitor and manage their digital assets on the platform digital wallet. Divi Project features are available for both Desktop and mobile devices.

The Divi Project coin (DIVI) is a cryptocurrencywhichmainnetwas launched on September 27th. It is now on the swapping process from DIVX to DIVI and as to the value,1 DIVX is being swapped for 100 DIVI.It uses a PoS (Proof of Stake) consensus algorithm and will serve the users as a medium to exchange value between them or to access goods and services available on Divi Project. DIVI features a second layer network of master nodes that process private and near-instant transactions.
